steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Database" with submenu "Database Editor"
Then I should see Database screen display
When I add new table with Name "jitapi002" and Comment "Testing"
Then I should see the table with Name "jitapi002" display
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolstring" Type "string" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoltext" Type "text" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolinteger" Type "integer" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolfloat" Type "float" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicolenum" Type "enum_type" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoldate" Type "date" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I add new column with Name "jitapicoldatetime" Type "datetime" for Table name "jitapi002" and verify
When I navigate to menu "API endpoints" with submenu "API endpoints editor"
Then I should see API screen display
When I wait query data API "jitapi002s.jitapicolstring" is fetched completely
When I select api name "jitapi002s" from list
When I toggle on API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi002s"
When I edit API method "GET" with endpoint "/api/jitapi002s"
Then I should see floating panel has method "GET"
Then I should see floating panel has endpoint "/api/jitapi002s"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with Name "filter"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with Model "jitapi002s"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "1" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicolstring","Start With","request.jitapi002s.jitapicolstring"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "2" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicoltext","Start With","request.jitapi002s.jitapicoltext"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "3" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicolinteger","Equal To","request.jitapi002s.jitapicolinteger"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "4" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicolfloat","Equal To","request.jitapi002s.jitapicolfloat"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "5" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicolenum","Equal To","request.jitapi002s.jitapicolenum"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "6" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicoldate","Equal To","request.jitapi002s.jitapicoldate"
Then I should see floating panel has Model - Query Table - row "7" - value "OR","jitapi002s.jitapicoldatetime","Equal To","request.jitapi002s.jitapicoldatetime"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with dropdown label "Page" has value "request.pagination_page"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with dropdown label "Limit" has value "request.pagination_limit"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with dropdown label "Order by" has value "jitapi002s.created_at"
Then I should see floating panel has Model with dropdown label "Order" has value "Desc"
When I click tab "Request params" in Params of floating panel
When I expand the row name "jitapi002s"
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "1" - value "jitapi002s","Object(JSON)".
Then I should see floating panel has Params - row "2" - value "jitapicolstring","String".
